\id HEB
\h Hibru
\toc1 Leta I Wa WeŇčgiya Hibru Jisas Gha Ghambu Utuniye
\toc2 Hibru
\toc3 Hib
\mt2 Leta I Wa WeŇčgiya
\mt1 Hibru
\mt2 Jisas Gha Ghambu
\mt2 Utuniye
\imt1 Utu iviva
\ip Letake iyake Jiu, iya thavala kaero th…® loŇčweghath…®gha Jisas, lenji leta. Jiu ghal…®Ňčanji vaŇča Hibru, iya kaiwae val…®kaiwae tembe raŇčava thiye Hibru ghar…®ghar…®niye. IyemaeŇčge ma ra ghareghare thela va i roriya letake iyake na i variye weŇčgi, na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva ma ra ghareghare wagiyawe raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko thiyako va inanji e the val…®vaŇčga. Ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya rarorori letake iyake va i rori theghathegha 60 na 70 A.D. e ghanjilughawoghawo, amba muyai Rom th…® tagarakaraka Ňägolo Boboma Jerusalem e t…®ne. MbaŇčako iyako Rom i mbaroŇča yambaneko wolagh…®ye.
\ip Thiye Jiu raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® th…® vaidiya v…®r…® lenji loŇčweghath…®ko kaiwae na vavana mbalama th…® rakanjogha Jiu e lenji kururu na lenji vowo e Ňägolo Boboma. Iya kaiwae rarorori i vaghareŇčgi Jisas iye i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye na amalagh…®niye Loi Nariye (VaŇčgothiye 1), ko iyemaeŇčge amalagh…®niye i tabo na lolo ghinda kaiwanda (VaŇčgothiye 2). Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya Mosese na Josuwa (3:1‚Äď4:13). I utuŇča na iŇča Jisas iye ravowovowo Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek na le kaiwoko i thovuye kivwalaŇčgiya ravowovowo me vivako lenji kaiwo. Jisas iye va i vamidiya dagerawe togha. Dagerawe teuye ma val…®kaiwae i vanamweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® rumwaru Loi e marae, ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas mbe ghamberegha vara e mad…®bae i vanamweinda (4:14‚Äď5:10 na 7:1‚Äď10:18). Iya kaiwae renuwaŇčake thiyake kaiwanji i vavur…®ghegheŇčgi na thava th…® njogha e ghereinji, ko iyemaeŇčge mbema th…® ghataŇčaghath…® eŇčge weinji lenji ghare matuwo th…® roroghagha iya thovuyeko Loi va i dageraweko kaiwanji (6:11-12 na 10:35-36, 39). I dage weŇčgi na val…®kaiwae ra vikikighath…® na val…®kaiwae ra vareminja Loi (10:23), na e marandake mbe ra vonjimbughath…® vara Jisas na ra ruku wagiyawe (12:1-3).
\c 1
\s1 Jisas, Loi Nariye, i Lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya Nyao Thovuthovuye
\p 
\v 1 Mevivako me mbaŇča tomethi na e kamwath…® tomethi t…®nenji, orumburumbunda th…® loŇčweya Loi le utu weŇčgiya ghal…®Ňčae gharautu,
\v 2 ko iyemaeŇčge e mbaŇčake iyake, iye mbaŇča momouniye, ra loŇčweya Loi le utu weya Nariye. Weya amalagh…®niye Loi va i vakathaŇčgiya yambaneke na buruburu, na iye Loi kaerova i tuthi na bigibigike wolagh…®ye inawe ne i mbaroŇča.
\v 3 Iye Loi le vwenyevwenye manjamanjalawae na iye Ňčgoreiye moliya Loi. Iye le utuutuko ele vur…®gheghe na i vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye mbe inanjiwe vara. Amalagh…®niye i mare na i thavwiyathu ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® ko mbaŇča i vakathavao iyako, i voro e buruburu na i yaku Loi Vur…®vur…®ghegheniye Moli val…®vaŇčga e uneko.
\v 4 Loi va i vakatha Nariye na i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, Ňčgoreiya idako iya Loi va i unogiyakowe i lagh…®ye kivwala nyao thovuthovuye idanji.
\p 
\v 5 Ňägoreiyako kaiwae Loi mava mbaŇča regha i dage weya le nyaoko thovuthovuye regha na iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄúGhen NaruŇčgwa ghen; na noroke ya tabona Raman…®na ghino.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Sam 2:7; 2Samu 7:14\x*
\m Na amalagh…®niye utuniye Loi tembe iŇčava:
\q1 ‚ÄúGhino ne ya tabo Ramae na amalagh…®niye NaruŇčgu.‚ÄĚ
\m 
\v 6 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mbaŇča Loi i variya Nariye ghagamau e yambaneke, amba iŇča, ‚ÄúLo nyaoko thovuthovuye wolagh…®ye ne th…® kururuwe.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:6 \xt Mba 32:43\x*
\m 
\v 7 Le nyao thovuthovuye kaiwanji Loi iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúYa vakathaŇčgiya lo nyao thovuthovuye rakakaiwo Ňčgoranjiya ndewendewe na nd…®ghe mamiye.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:7 \xt Sam 104:4\x*
\m 
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge Nariye utuniye iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúMbema Loiya ghen, len ghamba mbarona i meghabana ma ele ghambako;
\q1 wein ghan…®thanavu rumwaru u mbaroŇčaŇčgi na thovuye len ghar…®ghar…®.
\q1 
\v 9 U warariŇča thanavu i rumwaru na u botewoyathu thanavu raithar…®,
\q2 iya kaiwae wein len warari lagh…®ye, ghino len Loi ya liŇčgiya bunama e umbal…®na na ya vaŇčguraweŇčge u mbaroŇčaŇčgiya ghanunena.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:9 \xt Sam 45:6,7\x*
\m 
\v 10 Loi tembe i dageweva Nariye iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúGiya, va i rikowe ghen u vakatha yambaneke, na buruburuko ghen n…®man muiye.
\q1 
\v 11 Yambaneke na buruburu ne th…®ko, ko iyemaeŇčge ghen u meghabana.
\q2 Thiye ne th…® thar…® Ňčgoreiya kwama ghamb…®ghamb…® i ghamb…® na i vwatha.
\q1 
\v 12 Tene u vagh…®leŇčgi Ňčgoreiya th…® senisiya ghanjikwama.
\q1 Ko ghen ma u totomethi, na yawalina ma ele ghambako.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:12 \xt Sam 102:25-27\x*
\m 
\v 13 Loi ma mbaŇča regha i dage weya le nyao thovuthovuye regha na iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúU yaku gheke, val…®vaŇčga e uneŇčguke ghaghada ne ya biginjoŇčaŇčgiya ghan…®th…®gh…®ya e gheghen…®na raberabe.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Sam 110:1\x*
\m 
\v 14 Ko nyao thovuthovuye thavalaŇčgi? Thiye nyaoŇčgi th…® kaiwo weya Loi na i varivariye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® kaero th…® vaidiya vamoru na th…® thalavuŇčgi.
\c 2
\s1 Wo hu goruwe Loi ghal…®Ňčae
\p 
\v 1 Kaiwae Jisas i lagh…®ye kivwalaŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, wo ra vikikighath…®gha iya emunjoruko kaerova ra loŇčweko, mbala ma ra ghagha itete na ra bwagabwaga moliwe.
\v 2 Ra ghareghare mevivako nyao thovuthovuye meth…® utugiya Loi ghal…®Ňčae weya Mosese. Utuutuko iyako emunjoru na the ghar…®ghar…® th…® valaŇčaniya na ma th…® ghambu ne th…® vaidiya ghalith…® i mboromboro weiye lenji vakathako.
\v 3 Ne ŇčgoroŇčga raŇča na ra voiteta lith…®ko iyako thoŇčgo ma ra goru weya vamoruko utuniye? Giya mbe ghamberegha vara i govambwara weinda, thavala va th…® loŇčwe weya amalagh…®niye, th…® utuŇča ghaemunjoru weinda.
\v 4 Na Loi mbowo i vaemunjoruŇčava totoke iyake weinda ele vakatha e vakatha ghamba rotaele tomethi t…®nenji na i giya Nyao Boboma ghabebe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoreiya le renuwaŇča.
\s1 Jisas iye lolo, kin mara mbouye na ravowovowo lagh…®ye
\p 
\v 5 Loi mava i tuthiŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye na mbala th…® mbaroŇča yambane togha, iya ambane i vakathako na kaiwae wo rorori e ghemi.
\v 6 IyemaeŇčge Buk Boboma e t…®ne Sam ghararorori i woraŇčgiya lolo utuninda i dage weya Loi iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúLolo iye thela na Loi i rerenuwaŇča kaiwae? ŇägoroŇčga eŇčge na i thathalavu weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®?
\q1 
\v 7 Kaero u worawe na seiwo i yaku nyao thovuthovuye e raberabenji, kaero u vavwenyevwenye na u wovoreŇča idae,
\q1 
\v 8 na kaero u worawe ne i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Sam 8:4-6\x*
\m Bukuke iyake iŇča Loi kaerova i bigiraweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® mbaroŇčaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye, na gharumwaru Ňčgoreiye ma tembe bigi reghava inawe na mane ghar…®ghar…® th…® mbaroŇča. E mbaŇčake iyake ma ra thuwe ghar…®ghar…® th…® mbaroŇča bigibigike wolagh…®ye.
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas, iye va i tabo na lolo na seiwo i yaku nyao thovuthovuye e raberabenji, ra thuwe i mbaroŇčaŇčgiya bigibigike wolagh…®ye. I tabo na lolo amba Loi le mwaewo bwagabwaga e t…®ne iye i mare ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye kaiwanji. Va i ghataŇča v…®r…® na i mare amba Loi i vavwenyevwenye na i wovoreŇča idae.
\p 
\v 10 Loi va i vakatha bigibigike wolagh…®ye na bigibigike wolagh…®ye amalagh…®niye kaiwae. Amalagh…®niye nuwaiya i vaŇčguŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga lemoyo na i vavwenyevwenyeŇčgi, iyava i vakatha Jisas i tabona lolo na i vaidiya v…®r…® na e t…®ne val…®kaiwae i tabo lenji vamoruko r…®ghe na i ndeviva weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vaidiya vamoru. Val…®kaiwae moli Loi va i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako.
\v 11 Kaiwae iye Ravaboboma na weiyaŇčgiya thavala i vabobomaŇčgi Ramanji regha. Iya kaiwae ma i monjinaŇča ne iŇča oghaghaeŇčgi,
\v 12 na ne i dage weya Loi na iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúNe ya utuŇča ghan…®thanavuna weŇčgiya oghaghaŇčgu, na ya taraweŇčge e lenji mevathavatha t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:12 \xt Sam 22:22\x*
\m 
\v 13 Na tembe iŇčava: ‚ÄúGhino ya vareminja Loi,‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ais 8:17; 8:18\x* na mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúGhinoke iya weiŇčguyaŇčgiya Loi le ŇčgamaŇčgama iyava i giyake e ghino.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 14 Loi le ŇčgamaŇčgamako thiye mbun…®ma na madibe, na amalagh…®niye tembe Ňčgoreiyeva i tabo mbun…®ma na madibe Ňčgoreiya thiye. Va i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako mbala le mareko e t…®ne i mukuwo Seitan, kaiwae Seitan iye i mbaro mare ele val…®vaŇčga.
\v 15 Na e kamwath…®ke iyake Jisas i rakayathuŇčgiya thavala mbaŇča molao e yawalinjiko mare mararuniye i mbaroŇčaŇčgi.
\v 16 Emunjoru Jisas iye ma nyao thovuthovuye ghanjirathalavu Ňčgoreiye, ko iyemaeŇčge amalagh…®niye Eibraham orumburumbuye ghanjirathalavu.
\v 17 Iya kaiwae e bigibigike wolagh…®ye iye Ňčgoreiya oghaghaeŇčgi na val…®kaiwae Ňčgoreiya ravowovowo lagh…®ye. Iye i tabo ravowovowo lagh…®ye e ghavareminje na ghare weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko na i vakatha na i vamboromboro Loi le kaiwo, na iye i rakayathu ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®.
\v 18 Kaiwae amalagh…®niye va i vaidiya tanathetha na i ghataŇča v…®r…®, val…®kaiwae i thalavuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vavaidiya tanathetha.
\c 3
\s1 Jisas i lagh…®ye kivwala Mosese
\p 
\v 1 Iya kaiwae, lo bodaboda, ghemi Loi le ghar…®ghar…® na weiŇčguyaŇčgiya ghemi Loi i kula weinda ra rakawe, wo hu renuwaŇča Jisas kaiwae. Amalagh…®niye Loi ghal…®Ňčae gharaghamb…® na ravowovowo lagh…®ye iya raŇčama na ra loŇčweghath…®.
\v 2 Amalagh…®niye va i vakatha na i vamboromboro Loi le kaiwo Ňčgoreiya Mosese va i vamboromboro Loi le renuwaŇča na i kaiwo Loi ele Ňčgolo, iya Loi le ghar…®ghar…®.
\v 3 Ra ghareghare loloko iya i vatada Ňčgoloko iye e ghatarawa na Ňčgoloko ma e ghatarawa. Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva iyake, val…®kaiwae moli ra tarawe Jisas na raŇča iye idae i lagh…®ye kivwala Mosese idae.
\v 4 Ňägolo regha na regha mbe gharavakatha, na Loi iye bigibigike wolagh…®ye ghanjiravakatha.
\v 5 Mosese iye Loi le rakakaiwo, va i emunjoru ele kaiwoko t…®ne, i vamboromboro Loi le renuwaŇča na i kaiwo le ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji. Ghakaiwo i utuŇča bigibigi tene th…® yomara e manjamanjala utuninji.
\v 6 Ko iyemaeŇčge Krais iye Loi Nariye, kaero i vamboromboro Loi le renuwaŇča na iye Loi le Ňčgolo ghar…®ghar…®niye umbalinji. Ghinda Loi le Ňčgolo ghar…®ghar…®niye, thoŇčgo weinda la gharematuwo ra vareminje na weinda la warari ra roroghagha thovuyeko iyava i vivatharaweko kaiwanda.
\s1 RaloŇčweloŇčweghath…® ne th…® Towo
\p 
\v 7 Iya kaiwae, hu loŇčwe Nyao Boboma ghal…®Ňčae Ňčgoreiyake iŇča:
\q1 Noroke, thoŇčgo hu loŇčwe Loi ghal…®Ňčae,
\q1 
\v 8 thava gharemina i vur…®gheghe Ňčgoreiya orumburumbumi gharenji va i vur…®gheghe na th…® th…®gh…®ya wanaŇčgo.
\q1 MbaŇča lenji loŇčgaloŇčga e njamnjam…®bwaga, th…® wovanjovanjoŇčgo na lo ghataŇčaghath…® kaiwanji th…® mando.
\q1 
\v 9 Othembe va th…® thuweya lo vakatha theghathegha ghwevar…® e t…®ne ko iyemaeŇčge th…® wovanjovanjoŇčgo na th…® mandoŇčgo.
\q1 
\v 10 Thako iyako lenji vakathako kaiwae ya gaith…® wanaŇčgi, na ya utuutu kaiwanji yaŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake wolagh…®ye th…® botewoyathuŇčgo, na ma th…® ghambugha lo mbaro.‚ÄĚ
\q1 
\v 11 Iya kaiwae weiŇčgu lo gharegaith…® ya utuŇča dagerawe vur…®vur…®ghegheniye regha kaiwanji yaŇča, ‚ÄúMane th…® ru lo towoko e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 3:11 \xt Sam 95:7-11\x*
\p 
\v 12 Iya kaiwae, lo bodaboda, hu njimbukikiŇčga na thava regha e t…®nemina renuwaŇča raithar…® ina e ghare na i vakatha ma i loŇčweghath…®, ne iwaeŇčge i roghereiyewana Loi e yawayawaliye.
\v 13 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi thava hu vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, Ňčgoreiya Buku le utuutu iŇča: ‚ÄúMbaŇčake noroke,‚ÄĚ e mbaŇčake iyake ghamimbaŇča thovuye. Na mbaŇča regha na regha mbala hu veutu vavur…®gheghe weŇčga na thava thar…® thanavuniye i yarogha ghamu regha na ghare i vur…®gheghe.
\v 14 Ghinda Krais ghaune val…®ghareghare moli, thoŇčgo la loŇčweghath…® i vur…®gheghe Ňčgoreiya va i viva la loŇčweghath…®ma na ra vikikighath…® ghaghada mare ghambaŇča.
\v 15 Buku le utuutu iŇča Ňčgoreiyake:
\q1 ThoŇčgo hu loŇčweya ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu noroke thava gharemina i vur…®gheghe Ňčgoreiya orumburumbumi gharenji va i vur…®gheghe na th…® th…®gh…®ya wanaŇčgo.\x - \xo 3:15 \xt Sam 95:7,8\x*
\p 
\v 16 Thavala va th…® loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae ko iyemaeŇčge th…® goriwoyathu? Ko ana ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye iyava Mosese i vivako weŇčgi na th…® rakaraŇčgiko Ijipt e t…®ne?
\v 17 Thavala Loi va i gaith…®wanaŇčgi theghathegha ghwevar…® e t…®ne? Ko ana ghar…®ghar…®ko iyava th…® vakatha thar…®ko, na lenji thar…®ko kaiwae th…® mare bwagabwaga e njamnjam…®ko?
\v 18 Thavala Loi va i vakatha ghanjidagerawe vur…®vur…®ghegheniye na iŇča, ‚ÄúMane veth…® ru elo towoko t…®ne?‚ÄĚ Va i utuutu thavala mava th…® ghambugha ghal…®Ňčaeko kaiwanji.
\v 19 Ko ambama ra thuwe ma val…®kaiwanji th…® raka ru ele towoko t…®ne kaiwae mava th…® loŇčweghath…®.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Loi le dagerawema mbe inawe vara i yakuyaku, iya iŇčama val…®kaiwae ra ruwe na ra vaidiya towo weya amalagh…®niye. Iya kaiwae ra njimbukiki na thava ghemina regha Loi ne i tuthi itete na ma ve ru.
\v 2 Ra njimbukikinda kaiwae Toto Thovuye kaerova th…® utuŇča weinda na ra loŇčwe, Ňčgoreiya thiye va i vivako th…® loŇčweya Loi ghal…®Ňčae, ko iyemaeŇčge utuutuko iyako mava i thalavuŇčgi; kaiwae vambema th…® loŇčweŇčge, ko mava th…® loŇčweghath…®.
\v 3 Ghinda, thavala kaero ra loŇčweghath…®, ra ru na ra vaidiya towo. Towo utuniye iyava Loi iŇčake:
\q1 WeiŇčgu lo gaith…® ya utuŇča dagerawe vur…®vur…®ghegheniye kaiwanji na yaŇča, ‚ÄúMane th…® raka ru lo towoko e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:3 \xt Sam 95:11\x*
\m Loi va iŇča Ňčgoreiyako othembe budakaiya le renuwaŇča va iŇča ne i vakatha na kaerova i vakathavao mbaŇčaniye va i vakatha yambaneke.
\v 4 Kaiwae Buk Boboma e t…®ne rorori regha i utuuta mbaŇča ghepir…®niye kaiwae, iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča ghepir…®niye e t…®ne Loi i towowe ele vakathako wolagh…®ye.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:4 \xt R…®gh 2:2\x*
\v 5 Na Loi ghal…®Ňčae mbowo ra loŇčweva mbaŇčaiwoniye iya iŇčake, ‚ÄúMane th…® ru elo towoko t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 4:5 \xt Sam 95:11\x*
\p 
\v 6 Emunjoru ghar…®ghar…® vavana ne th…® raka ru Loi le towo e t…®ne, na emunjoru me vivako me th…® loŇčweya Loi le utu mava th…® raka ru, lenji goriwoyathu kaiwae.
\v 7 Iyake kaiwae Loi mbowo i woraweva mbaŇča regha, iya kaiwae iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇčake noroke.‚ÄĚ Theghathegha lemoyo e ghereiye amba Loi tembe i ravair…®va utuutuke iyake weya Deivid, Ňčgoreiya mbema ma utuŇčama, iŇča:
\q1 MbaŇčake noroke, thoŇčgo ghino Loi ghal…®ŇčaŇčgu i raŇčgi weŇčga, thava gharemina i vur…®gheghe.\x - \xo 4:7 \xt Sam 95:7,8\x*
\m 
\v 8 ThoŇčgo Josuwa va i giya towo weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® Ňčgoreiya Loi le dageraweko weŇčgi, mbala ma tembe i utuutuva mbaŇča regha kaiwae.
\v 9 Iya kaiwae ra ghareghare towo mbe inawe vara Loi le ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji Ňčgoreiya Loi le towo ghambaŇča, mbaŇča ghepir…®niye.
\v 10 Kaiwae thoŇčgo lolo regha i ru e towoko iya Loi va i dageraweko e t…®ne, iye kaero i towo ele kaiwo t…®ne, Ňčgoreiya va i rikowe Loi va i towo ele kaiwo t…®ne.
\p 
\v 11 Iya kaiwae wo ra rovur…®gheghe lagh…®ye na ra ru varathuwe towoko iyako, na thava ghindake regha i dobu kaiwae ma i ghambugha Loi le utu, Ňčgoreiya thiye mevivako mava th…® ghambu.
\v 12 Loi ghal…®Ňčae iye e yawayawaliye na ele vur…®gheghe, i lawe moli, na i lawe kivwala gaith…® ghaghalith…® marae vaŇčga na vaŇčga. Utuutuko iyako i ru maya moli, na i vothewo gharenda na unenda Ňčgoreiya kaina i lawe moli i vothewo riwandake Ňčginauye na vuvuye. Iye i ghatha gharendake gham…®nae na le renuwaŇča.
\v 13 Loi i ghareghareya bigibigiko wolagh…®ye ghar…®ghar…® wolagh…®ye kaiwanji na ma bigi regha i rothuwele Loi e marae. Weya amalagh…®niye bigibigike wolagh…®ye i mavu na i manjalawe, na nevole ra ndeghath…® e marae na i vanivaŇčainda la vakatha kaiwae.
\s1 Jisas iye la ravowovowo lagh…®ye
\p 
\v 14 Wo ra vikikighath…® la loŇčweghath…®ko iya ra uturaŇčgiyako kaiwae la ravowovowo lagh…®ye kaero inawe, na iye kaerova ve ru e buruburu, iye Jisas, Loi Nariye.
\v 15 La ravowovowo lagh…®ye amalagh…®niye val…®kaiwae moli e la njavovoke ne ghare i njaweinda, kaiwae va i vaidivao tanathethako wolagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya ghinda, ko iyemaeŇčge mava i vakatha thar…®.
\v 16 Mbema weindaeŇčge la gharematuwo ra wa weya Loi vur…®vur…®ghegheniye, iye ragharemwaewo. Na thoŇčgo e ghandavuyowo, iye ghare ne i njaweinda na weiye le mwaewo bwagabwaga i thalavuinda.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye regha na regha ghatututhi i mena weŇčgiya le val…®ravowovowo, na i kaiwo Loi le ghar…®ghar…® kaiwanji. Iye i mbana ghar…®ghar…® lenji mwaewo na i vakatha vowo lenji thar…® kaiwae.
\v 2 Iye val…®kaiwae ghathanavu i udauda weŇčgiya ranumounouno na thavala ma th…® ghareghare iyaŇčganiya thovuye, kaiwae amalagh…®niye tembe ele njavovova.
\v 3 Iyake kaiwae mbaŇča i vowo tembe i vowova amalagh…®niye na ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® kaiwae.
\p 
\v 4 Bigi reghava, ma val…®kaiwae lolo regha tembe ghamberegha i wovoreŇča na i tabo ravowovowo lagh…®ye. Loi ghamberegha i kula weya loloko iyako na i tabo ravowovowo lagh…®ye, Ňčgoreiya va i kula weya Eron.\f + \fr 5:4 \ft Eron iye iviva moli i tabo na ravowovowo lagh…®ye.\f*
\v 5 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Krais. Mava i wovoreŇča ghamberegha na mbala i tabo na ravowovowo lagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi va i wovoreŇča e ghamba yakuko iyako. Loi kaerova i dagevaowe iŇča:
\q1 ‚ÄúGhen naruŇčgwa ghen, noroke ya tabo na Raman…®na ghino.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Sam 2:7\x*
\m 
\v 6 Na tembe inava e Buk Boboma regha t…®ne i dagewe iŇča: ‚ÄúGhen mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako ne u tabo ravowovowo Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek iye va ravowovowo.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 5:6 \xt Sam 110:4\x*
\p 
\v 7 MbaŇča Jisas vamba ina e yambaneke le naŇčgo e t…®ne e ghareko lagh…®ye i kula voro weya Loi weiye le randa na val…®kaiwae i vamoru e mare. Loi va i loŇčweya le naŇčgoko, kaiwae i gharenja na i vareminja Loi.
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge othembe va i naŇčgo na Ňčgoreiyako na othembe iye Loi Nariye, va i ghataŇča v…®r…® na i mare, na e t…®ne val…®kaiwae i ghareghareya Loi ghal…®Ňčae ghaghambu.
\v 9 Kaiwae i vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, i vaemunjoruŇča moli iye val…®kaiwae moli i giya vamoru memeghabananiye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye iya thavala th…® ghambu ghal…®Ňčae.
\v 10 Na iyako e vwatae, Loi kaerova i vaemunjoruŇča na i tabo ravowovowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek iye va ravowovowo lagh…®ye.
\s1 Lemi loŇčweghath…® weya Krais ne hu ndeviyathu
\p 
\v 11 Bigibigi lemoyo mbe inanjiwe nuwameiya wo utuŇča Krais kaiwae, iye ravowovowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek, ko iyemaeŇčge i vuyowo ne wo vamanjamanjalaŇča weŇčga kaiwae lemi gharegharena i vuyowo.
\v 12 Vambe teuye val…®kaiwami hu tabo ravavaghare na hu vavaghare weŇčgiya ghamune, iyemaeŇčge lemi ghareghare amba ma i lagh…®ye, na renuwaŇča iviva moli Loi le utuutu kaiwae lolo regha wo i vaghareŇčga. Ghemi Ňčgoramiya Ňčgama gunagunagha, amba thu vara i ndewoŇčga, na amba ma val…®kaiwami hu ghana ghan…®Ňčga vur…®gheghe.
\p 
\v 13 Thavala amba th…® thuthu, thiye gamagai gunagunagha na amba ma e lenji ghareghare iyaŇčganiya i rumwaru na iyaŇčganiya i thar…®.
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghan…®Ňčga vur…®gheghe ghar…®ghar…® matuwo kaiwanji, na thiye kaiwae tembe ghanjimberegha kaero th…® vaghareŇčgi val…®kaiwanji th…® tuthiya thovuye na thar…®.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 Iya kaiwae wo ra ghao eŇčge e ghamwandako na ra wo vavaghareko iya val…®kaiwae i vaghare matuwoŇčaindako na wo ra viyathu budakaiya vama th…® vaghareinda Krais kaiwae. Thava tembe ra vair…®va utuutuko iya ra ndeghereiyewana vakathako i womena mareko na mbema ra loŇčweghath…® eŇčge Loi.
\v 2 Kaerova th…® vaghareinda bap…®taiso kaiwae na ekelesiya gharandeviva th…® bigiraweya n…®manji e umbal…®nda. Kaero ra ghareghareya ramaremare tembene th…® thuweiruva mare e t…®ne na ghatha ghambaŇča e mbaŇča momouniye. Bigibigike thiyake ma val…®kaiwae ra vair…®va.
\v 3 Mbema ra ghawoeŇčge e ghamwandako thoŇčgo Loi le renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye.
\p 
\v 4 ThoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® kaerova Loi manjamanjalawae i woya weŇčgi, na kaerova th…® gham…®nogha Loi le mwaewo gham…®nae na weinjiyaŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ke wolagh…®ye kaero th…® wo Nyao Boboma,
\v 5 na Loi le utuutu weŇčgi kaerova th…® gham…®nogha gham…®nae, na kaerova th…® gham…®no ghavur…®ghegheko iya Loi ne i vakaiwoŇčako mbaŇča muyaiko,
\v 6 na thoŇčgo kaero th…® roiteta lenji loŇčweghath…® weya Krais na th…® botewoyathu, kaero ma val…®kaiwae tembe ra vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgiva na th…® ndeghereiyewana lenji thar…®ko, iyako Ňčgoreiya tembe th…® rokros…®va Loi Nariye na th…® vamonjinaŇča ghar…®ghar…® e maranji.
\p 
\v 7 NuwaŇčguiya hu thuwe raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® Ňčgoreiya uma. ThoŇčgo uye i nja valaŇča ele thelauko na une i thovuye, Loi ne i mwaewowe.
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo kavwala na nana raraithar…® th…® mbuthuwe ma e ghathovuye na kaero Loi i gura na le ghambako venda e nd…®ghe une.
\p 
\v 9 Ko iyemaeŇčge, ghamaune val…®ghareghareme, othembe thoŇčgo wo utuŇčaŇčgiya utuutu e gham…®nanji e ghemi, ghareme mbe i matuwo eŇčge e ghemi. Wo ghareghare wagiyawe kaero hu vur…®mban e kamwath…®ko iya val…®kaiwae thavala Loi kaero i vamoru.
\v 10 Loi iye i rumwaru, na mane i renuwaŇča vaghalawa iya kaiwona hu vakathana o iya lemi gharethovu amalagh…®niye kaiwaena ve raŇčgi e lemi thalavuna na mbe hu thalathalavuna weŇčgiya lemi val…®raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®.
\v 11 Nuwameiya moli ghemi regha na regha mbe hu vikikighath…® vara iya vakathako iyako ghaghad yawalimi ele ghambako, mbala lemi gharematuwona i vur…®gheghe na hu roroghagha thovuyeko iya Loi va i dageraweko kaiwanda.
\v 12 Ma nuwameiya hu njavovo, ko iyemaeŇčge ghamithanavuna Ňčgoreiya thavala th…® loŇčweghath…® na th…® ghataŇčaghath…® kaiwae lenji vakathako une th…® wo budakaiya Loi va i dagerawe kaiwanji.
\s1 Loi le dagerawe ne i emunjoru
\p 
\v 13 Ghamba thuwathuwa regha iyake: MbaŇča Loi i utuŇča le dagerawe weya Eibraham, mava tembe lolo reghava iye idae i lagh…®ye kivwala amalagh…®niye na val…®kaiwae i tholo e idae, vambema i wo amalagh…®niyeko idae na i tholowe.
\v 14 IŇča, ‚ÄúYa dagerawe emunjoru ne ya mwaewo e ghen na orumburumbu nevole lemoyo.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 6:14 \xt R…®gh 22:17\x*
\v 15 Eibraham vambe i ghataŇčaghath…® vara na i roroghagha tevambema i woeŇčge Loi le dageraweko une.
\p 
\v 16 MbaŇča ghar…®ghar…® ghinda nuwandaiya ra tholo, ra tholo lolo lagh…®ye regha e idae, na i vaemunjoruŇča la tholoko mbema emunjoru, na i kitena wogaith…®ko.
\v 17 Loi va nuwaiya i vaemunjoruŇča le dageraweko, iya kaiwae va nuwaiya ra ghareghare wagiyawe ma tene i v…®v…®va le renuwaŇča, thavala th…® wo le dageraweko ne th…® vaidi une.
\v 18 Dageraweko na tholoko mbe th…® yaku vara, th…® roghabana na ma val…®kaiwae Loi ne i kwan kaiwanji. Iya kaiwae thavala ghinda kaerova ra voru Loi e ghadidiye, val…®kaiwae ra wo vur…®gheghewe weinda la gharematuwo na ra roroghagha thovuyeko iya e ghamwandako.
\v 19 Thovuyeko iyako ghagharematuwo Ňčgoreiya yawalindake ghayaŇčge, i laweghath…®inda na ra yaku na thovuye la yaŇčgeko le ghamba lawe iye Loi, iye ina i yaku Ghamba Yaku Bobomako Moli e t…®ne, iya th…® ligana e kwamako, ina maya mevathavatha Ňčgoloniyeko e t…®ne.
\v 20 Jisas iye i viva e ghamwanda na ve ru e Ghamba Yaku Bobomako Moli t…®ne, kaiwae i tabo ravowovowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek na iye ravowovowo mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\c 7
\s1 Ravowovowo Melkisedek utuniye
\p 
\v 1 Melkisedek iye ghemba Salem ghakiŇč na iye Loi Ramevoro Moli le ravowovowo. MbaŇča Eibraham weiyaŇčgiya kiŇč…®ma theghevar…®ma th…® gaith…® na i kivwalaŇčgi, kaero i njoghanjogha e ghemba, Melkisedek i lavolevole na i dagewe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi ghare e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\v 2 Amba Eibraham i tena bigibigiko wolagh…®ye va ve mban…®ko na i vakatha wabwiyaworo na i giya wabwira weya Melkisedek. Idake Melkisedek gharumwaru ‚ÄúThanavu Rumwarumwaruniye ghakiŇč,‚ÄĚ na idae reghava ‚ÄúSalem lenji kiŇč,‚ÄĚ gharumwaru ‚ÄúVanevane gha KiŇč.‚ÄĚ
\v 3 Melkisedek ramae na t…®nae mava th…® rori mun ghanjiriuriu, na le vir…® na le mare ma tembe e utuutuniyeva. Amalagh…®niye Ňčgoreiya Loi Nariye, i tabo ravowovowo mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\p 
\v 4 Wo hu thuwe Melkisedek idae i lagh…®ye moli. Ghinda rumbunda lagh…®ye Eibraham bigibigima va i mban e gaith…®ko t…®ne i ten na wabwiyaworo na i giya wabwira weya Melkisedek.
\v 5 Thiye uu Livai th…® tabo na ravowovowo, na mbaro va iŇča Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niyeko wolagh…®ye tembe th…® ten…®va lenji bigibigiko wabwiyaworo na th…® giya wabwi regha weŇčgiya uu Livai. Iyake i emunjoru othembe thiye oghaghanjiŇčgiya uu Livai na ghanjiriuriu i mena weya Eibraham, va th…® vakavakatha Ňčgoreiyako.
\v 6 Ko iyemaeŇčge othembe Melkisedek iye ma Livai rumbuye Ňčgoreiye va i mbana bigibigiko ghawabwi regha weya Eibraham, na Eibraham iye ghadagerawe i mena weya Loi, va i dage mwaewowe iŇča, ‚ÄúLoi i mwaewo e ghen.‚ÄĚ
\v 7 Ma ra numoghegheiwoŇča loloko i giya dagemwaewoko i lagh…®ye kivwala iya i wo dagemwaewoko.
\p 
\v 8 Na bigi reghava, ravowovowo uu Livai e t…®ne iya th…® mban…®mba wabwi regha weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye, tenevole th…® mare, ko iyemaeŇčge Melkisedek, iye va i mbana wabwi regha weya Eibraham, ma e utuutuniye na i mare.
\v 9 Na val…®kaiwae tembe raŇčava Ňčgoreiyake. Uu Livai th…® mban…®mba wabwi regha weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye, ko mbaŇča Eibraham i giya wabwi regha weya Melkisedek, iyako Ňčgoreiya uu Livai th…® giya.
\v 10 Val…®kaiwae ra utu Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae mbaŇča Melkisedek i vaidiya Eibraham, Livai vama ina weya rumbuye Eibraham, vamba ina eŇčge e mad…®bae na vamba ma i yomara.
\s1 Jisas Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek na i kivwalaŇčgiya ravowovowo mevivako
\p 
\v 11 Mosese va i giya Mbaro weŇčgiya Isirel ghar…®ghar…®niye na ravowovowo uu Livai e t…®ne th…® njimbukikiya Mbaroko iyako kaiwoniye. Ghar…®ghar…® th…® renuwaŇča Mbaro ne i varumwaruŇčgi. Ko iyemaeŇčge ma val…®kaiwanji th…® vakathaŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® na th…® rumwaru, amba Loi iŇča na ravowovowo mbe tomethi regha i yomara, iye ma Ňčgoreiya Eron, ko mbe ravowovowova Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek iye ravowovowo.
\v 12 Na thoŇčgo ravowovowo ma reghaova i yomara, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva mbaro ma reghaova i yomara.
\v 13 Ghanda Giyake iya ra utuuta utuniyeke, iye mbe uu regha loloniye na ma mbaŇča regha uuko iyako loloniye i tabo na ravowovowo na ma i vakatha mun vowo kakaiwoniye e ghamba vowo.
\v 14 Kaero ra ghareghare ghanda Giya va i yomara Juda e gheuu t…®ne na Mosese mava i utuŇča mun uuko iyako loloniye regha ne i tabo ravowovowo.
\p 
\v 15 Budakai ma utuuta utuniyema noroke kaero i wowoya, ravowovowo ma reghaova regha kaero i yomara, iye Ňčgoreiya Melkisedek.
\v 16 Ma kaiwae i vamboromboroŇča Loi le mbaro na i tabo ravowovowo, ko iyemaeŇčge va i tabona ravowovowo kaiwae vur…®ghegheko iya e yawaliyeko, mane mbaŇča regha ikoko.
\v 17 Kaiwae Buku Boboma e t…®ne iŇča, ‚ÄúGhen ne u tabo ravowovowo mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako, Ňčgorana Melkisedek iye ravowovowo.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 7:17 \xt Sam 110:4\x*\fig Ravowovowo ma reghaova regha kaero i yomara, iye Ňčgoreiye Melkisedek|alt="priest at altar" src="hk00260c.tif" size="col" copy="BFBS (Knowles)" ref="7:15"\fig*
\p 
\v 18 Iya kaiwae mbaro teuye kaero ma ele vur…®gheghe na ma val…®kaiwae i vakatha Ňčgoreiya gharerenuwaŇčako na ma e ghathovuye,
\v 19 kaiwae Mosese le Mbaro ma i vakatha bigi regha na i rumwaru. Na Loi kaerova i giya la gharematuwo regha na iyako i thovuye kivwala Mbaro, na e la gharematuwoko iyako ra mena Loi evasiwae.
\p 
\v 20 Na mbowo bigi reghava, mbaŇča Loi i tuthiya Jisas na i tabo ravowovowo, mava i worawe bwagabwaga, ko iyemaeŇčge va weiye le tholo. MbaŇča uu Livai gh…®mogh…®moruniye th…® tabo na ravowovowo mava e tholo,
\v 21 ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča Jisas va i tabona ravowovowo, Loi va i tholo. Buku Boboma iŇča Ňčgoreiyake:
\q1 ‚ÄúGiya kaerova i tholo na mane i v…®va le renuwaŇča, iŇča,
\q1 ‚ÄėMbaŇčake wolagh…®ye na ma ele ghambako ghen ne Ňčgorana ravowovowo.‚Äô‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 7:21 \xt Sam 110:4\x*
\m 
\v 22 Loi le tholoko kaiwae Jisas i tabo ravowovowo, iya kaiwae ra ghareghare wagiyawe Jisas iye dagerawe thovuye i kivwala dagerawe teuye ghathovuye na iye i vaemunjoruŇča gharerenuwaŇča na ghinda ra vaidiya une.
\p 
\v 23 Na reghava, mevivako ravowovowo th…® mena uu Livai me lemoyo, kaiwae regha na regha mare va i kiten na ma val…®kaiwae i kaiwombela ghakaiwoko.
\v 24 Ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas ghambaŇča i tabo ravowovowo, i roghabana moli na ma e ghath…®th…®.
\v 25 Iya kaiwae val…®kaiwae moli noroke na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ne i vamoruŇčgiya thavala th…® mena weya Loi amalagh…®niye e idae kaiwae yawaliye ma ele ghambako na mbe i naŇčgonaŇčgo ghanjithalavu kaiwae.
\p 
\v 26 Kaiwae ravowovowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiyako i vamboromboro la renuwaŇča. Amalagh…®niye i boboma, ma e ghawonjowe, i kakaleva, i meghaghath…® weŇčgiya thar…® gharavakatha, na Loi kaerova i vaŇčguvoreŇča yavoro moli na ve yaku e buruburu.
\v 27 Iye ma Ňčgoreiya ravowovowo lagh…®ye mevivako. MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye mane mbowo i vakathakai eŇčge vowo amalagh…®niye le thar…® kaiwae, Ňčgoreiya ravowovowo iya th…® mena uu Livai, ko amba muyai i vowo ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® kaiwae. Amalagh…®niye vambe ghamberegha vara i vatomwe ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® vowoniye, na vambe mbaŇčara eŇčge i vakatha mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye kaiwae.
\v 28 Mosese le Mbaro va i bigiraweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®, thiye th…® njavovo, th…® tabo ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye. Ko iyemaeŇčge Mbaroko iyako e ghereiye Loi i tholo na iŇča Nariye i tabo na ravowovowo lagh…®ye; iye ghathanavu i rumwaru mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\c 8
\s1 Jisas iye la ravowovowo lagh…®ye
\p 
\v 1 Lama renuwaŇča lagh…®ye moli na kaiwae wo utuutu Ňčgoreiyake: la ravowovowo lagh…®ye Ňčgoreiyako mbe inawe. Amalagh…®niye kaerova i voro e buruburu na i yaku Loi Ravwenyevwenye Moli ele ghamba yaku val…®vaŇčga e uneko.
\v 2 Iye ravowovowo lagh…®ye e Ňčgolo boboma e buruburu, Ňčgoloko iyako iye Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye emunjoru moli Loi va i vatad, na mava ghar…®ghar…® th…® vatad.
\p 
\v 3 Ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye regha na regha ghakaiwo i mban…®mba ghar…®ghar…® lenji mwaewo na i vakatha lenji thar…® vowoniye weya Loi. Na ghinda la ravowovowo lagh…®ye tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, iye tembe i vowova bigi regha weya Loi.
\v 4 ThoŇčgo mbe ina e yambaneke, mbala ma i tabo ravowovowo, kaiwae ravowovowo vambe inanji gheke th…® vakavakatha vowo Ňčgoreiya Mbaro le woraŇčgiya.
\v 5 Ravowovowoke thiyake th…® kaiwo e Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e yambaneke Ňčgoreiya buruburu ŇčgaliŇčgaliya. Iyake kaiwae, mbaŇča Mosese nuwaiya i vatada Mevathavatha gha Ňägolo, Loi i dage vur…®gheghewe iŇča, ‚ÄúU njimbukiki na thovuye na ghavatavatad Ňčgoreiya va ya vaghareŇčgema e ouko vwatae.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 8:5 \xt RaŇč 25:40\x*\fig Th…® kaiwo e Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye e yambaneke Ňčgoreiya buruburu ŇčgaliŇčgaliya|alt="layout of tabernacle tents" src="lb00259c.tif" size="span" copy="BFBS (Bass)" ref="8:5"\fig*
\v 6 Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi kaerova i tuthiya Jisas na iye i tabo ravowovowo, na le kaiwoko iyako i kivwalaŇčgiya ravowovowo lagh…®lagh…®ye me vivako lenji kaiwo. Dageraweko iya amalagh…®niye va i vamidiko ghar…®ghar…® na Loi e ghanjilughawoghawo i thovuye kivwala dagerawe teuye, kaiwae Loi va i woraweya vaemunjoruko iyako na i dagerawe ghar…®ghar…® ne th…® vaidiya ghathovuye lagh…®ye moli.
\p 
\v 7 ThoŇčgova dageraweko teuye mava e ghathar…® regha mun mbala dagerawe togha ma tembe e gharerenuwaŇčava.
\v 8 Ko iyemaeŇčge Loi i thuwe vaidiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® amba i dageraweya dagerawe togha kaiwae, i dage Ňčgoreiyake:
\q1 Giya iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča i menamenako ne ya vakatha dagerawe togha wabwi Isirel na wabwi Judiya kaiwanji.
\q1 
\v 9 Dageraweke iyake ma Ňčgoreiya iyava ya vakathako weŇčgiya orumburumbunji mbaŇčaniye ya v…®ghath…® e n…®manji na ya vaŇčgu raŇčgiyaŇčgi Ijipt e t…®ne.
\q1 Ko iyemaeŇčge thiye mava th…® ghambugha dageraweko iyava ya vakathako iyako le utuutu, iya kaiwae ghino Giya ya wogiya ghereiŇčgu weŇčgi.
\q1 
\v 10 Iya dageraweko ne ya rovakathako wabwi Isirel kaiwanji ne Ňčgoreiyake:
\q1 Ne ya woraweya lo mbaro e lenji renuwaŇčako t…®ne na th…® ghareghare na ya rori e gharenji na th…® ghambu. Ghino ne ya tabo lenji Loi na thiye th…® tabo lo ghar…®ghar…®.
\q1 
\v 11 Na mbala ma val…®kaiwae, lolo regha tembe i vavaghare weva gheu regha Giya kaiwae, o regha i dage weya ghaghae na iŇča, ‚ÄėGhen mbala u ghareghareya Giya,‚Äô kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ne th…® ghareghareŇčgo, othembe thiye mbema ghar…®ghar…® bwagaeŇčge o thoŇčgo e idaidanji.
\q1 
\v 12 Kaiwae lenji vakathako raraithar…® ne ya numoten, na lenji thar…®ko mane tembe ya renuwaŇčakikiva.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 8:12 \xt Jer 31:31-34\x*
\p 
\v 13 MbaŇča Loi i utuŇča dageraweko togha kaiwae, e kamwath…®ko dageraweko iyava i vakatha i vivako kaero i teuye. Na the bigiya kaero i teuye na i vwatha mbaŇča nasiye iko moli.
\c 9
\s1 Loi ghakururu e yambaneke na e buruburu
\p 
\v 1 Dagerawe teuye ghambaro vavana va inanjiwe kururu ghavakavakatha kaiwae, na ghaŇčgolo boboma vambe th…® vatad…®va e yambaneke.
\v 2 MbaŇča va th…® vamidiya Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye, th…® livakwata kwama yaŇčgara na ghath…®n…®mba. E t…®ne woluwolu iviva idae Woluwolu Boboma. E t…®ne kad…®ŇčeŇče weiye ghambanji na tebol weiye bred boboma kaero th…® vowo weya Loi.
\v 3 Kwama yaŇčgaiwoniye th…® livakwate e woluwolu reghava na woluwoluko iyako idae Woluwolu Boboma Moli.
\v 4 E Woluwolu Bobomako Moli iyako e t…®ne inisen…®s\f + \fr 9:4 \ft Inisen…®s iye umbwa thiye butiye thovuye na modanji lagh…®ye moli.\f* ghaghamba ŇčambuŇčambu va th…® vakatha e gol na dagerawe ghabogis. Va th…® monja gol iya e dageraweko ghabogis riwaeko lagh…®ye, na e t…®ne th…® bigimbana bigibigi theghetowe: ghan…®Ňčga manna ghauye th…® vakatha e gol, Eron le umbwa kaero i mbuthuva na i rau, na var…® debedebenai var…®iwo thovuthovuye iyava Loi i roriya dageraweko teuye ghautuutu e vwatanji.
\v 5 E bogisiko vwatae nyao thovuthovuye theghewo th…® wo Loi vwenyevwenyewaeko, vineinjiko i garubwa lughawoghawoko iya thar…®ko ghaghamba raka. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇčake ma ghambaŇča na wo uturaŇčgiya nasiye na lagh…®ye.\fig Dagerawe gha Bogis ghayamoyamo Ňčgoraiyake|alt="ark of covenant" src="Ark.tif" size="col" copy="SIL-PNG" ref="9:4-5"\fig*
\p 
\v 6 Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye na bigibiginiyeko ghanjivakatha va Ňčgoreiyevarako. Na mbaŇča regha na regha ravowovowo th…® ruru e woluwoluko iya i vivako na th…® vakavakatha ghanjikaiwo kururu kaiwae.
\v 7 Ko iyemaeŇčge mbe ravowovowo lagh…®ye eŇčge ghamberegha i ruru e woluwoluko iya theghewoniyeko t…®ne. Theghathagha umbwara e t…®ne mbe mbaŇčara eŇčge vara i ruwe. Na ma val…®kaiwae i ru bwagabwaga, ko mbe i th…®na madibe amalagh…®niye le thar…® kaiwae na ghar…®ghar…® tembe lenji thar…®va kaiwae, iyava th…® vakathako na lenji renuwaŇča th…®ŇčaeŇčge ma thar…® Ňčgoreiye.
\v 8 Woluwolu i vivama mbe ina e ghambae iya kaiwae amba ma kamwath…® i mavu na val…®kaiwae ghar…®ghar…® th…® ru na th…® wa e Woluwolu Bobomako Moli t…®ne. Iyake Nyao Boboma i vaghareinda iyako, mbaŇča dagerawe teuye mbe ina e ghambae ma tembe kamwath…®va na ghar…®ghar…® th…® reŇčawe na veth…® ru Loi e marae.
\v 9 Iyako Ňčgoreiya goghaimba mbaŇčake iyake i yoyomara kaiwae. E mbaŇčake iyake mbe th…® vakavakatha rakurukururu lenji mwaewo na th…® vowoŇčaŇčgiya thetheghan, ko iyemaeŇčge vakathake iyake ma val…®kaiwae i vanamwe ghar…®ghar…® gharenji na th…® rumwaru,
\v 10 kaiwae vakathake iyake weiye ghan…®Ňčga, munumu na thithu, ghanjimbaro na ghanjirerenuwaŇča mbe i reŇča eŇčge e ririwo. Vakathako iyako mbe ghanjimbaŇča, na i mena ghaghad mbaŇčake Loi kaerova i vugha kamwath…® togha.
\s1 Krais mad…®bae
\p 
\v 11 Krais kaerova i mena na iye ravowovowo lagh…®ye, na kaerova i womena thovuyeke iyake. I ghathara Mevathavathako gha Ňägolo iya i lagh…®ye kivwala teuyeko na i thovuye moli; mava ghar…®ghar…® th…® vatad e n…®manji na ma yambaneke Ňčgoloniye Ňčgoreiye.
\v 12 MbaŇčara na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye kaiwae amalagh…®niye kaerova i ru e Woluwolu Bobomako Moli t…®ne. Ma raŇčava va i th…®na burumwaka na gout mad…®banji na i ru, ko iyemaeŇčge mbe amalagh…®niye vara ghamberegha e mad…®bae i vamodo njoghainda thar…® e t…®ne mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\p 
\v 13 ThoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® th…® mbigh…® Loi e marae Ňčgoreiya lenji kururu ghambaro, ravowovowo i th…®na gout na burumwaka gh…®moru mad…®banji o i th…®na burumwaka wevo th…® Ňčambu na vughauye weiye mbwa na i tagaseura ghar…®ghar…®ko thiyako riwanjiwe. I vakatha ghar…®ghar…®ko riwanji i th…®na na mbigh…®wanjiko iko.
\v 14 Ko iyemaeŇčge Krais mad…®bae i thovuye kivwalaŇčgiya thiyako. Nyao Memeghabananiye le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne Krais tembe ghamberegha vara i vatomwe na i mare na vowo weya Loi. Amalagh…®niye mad…®baeko iya i thavwiyathu la vakatha vathar…®ko mbigh…®wae iya modaya mareko, i vanamwe gharenda na i kakaleva. I vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na ra tabo rakakaiwo weya Loi e yawayawaliye.
\p 
\v 15 Krais va i vanamwe dagerawe togha r…®ghethoru kaiwae mbala thavala kaerova Loi i kula weŇčgi th…® vaidiya thovuyeko iya memeghabananiyeko iyava i dageraweko. Val…®kaiwae ra wo dageraweko iyako kaiwae le mare kaerova i yomara, na le mareko iyako i rakayathuŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®, iyava th…® vakathako mbaŇča vamba inanji dageraweko teuye e raberabe.
\p 
\v 16 ThoŇčgo amala regha i dagerawe weya nariye na ne i robigiya le bigibigiko vavana le mare e ghereiye, ma val…®kaiwae nariye i mbana dageraweko iyako bigibiginiyeko ghaghada amalako i mare.
\v 17 Kaiwae thoŇčgo amalako iyako amba e yawayawaliye, dageraweko iyako amba i yaku bwagabwaga. Wone mare i yomara ambane dagerawe Ňčgoreiyako i tabo emunjoru.
\v 18 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva iyake, dagerawe teuye mava th…® vaemunjoru bwagabwaga, vambowo thetheghan i mare na e madibewaeko amba i vaemunjoruŇča.
\v 19 Va th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyake. Mosese va i utugiya Mbaroko utuutuniye wolagh…®ye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye. Kaero i th…®na burumwaka mad…®banji weiye mbwa, tembe Ňčgoreiyeva i liya thiyo sosoro th…® vakatha sip vulivuliye na nana hisop yaŇčgae, amba i vaŇčguthiya e madibema na i variriya Mbaro ghabuk na ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye.
\v 20 Amba Mosese iŇča, ‚ÄúMadibeke iyake i vaemunjoruŇča dageraweko iyava Loi iŇčake hu ghambu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 9:20 \xt RaŇč 24:8\x*
\v 21 Mosese vambe i vakathava Ňčgoreiyako, va i th…®na madibe na i variriya Mevathavathako Ňägoloniye na bigibigiko iyava th…® vakaiwoŇčaŇčgiko kururu kaiwae.
\v 22 Ňägoreiye, Mbaro iŇča bigibigiko wolagh…®ye th…® vakatha na i th…®na e madibe na mbigh…®ko iko moli. Na Loi mane i numotena thar…® thoŇčgo madibe ma i voru.
\p 
\v 23 Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye iye bigiko iya emunjoruko moli ina e buruburu ŇčgaliŇčgaliya. Val…®kaiwae moli tembe th…® vabobomaŇčava bigibigiko Ňčgoreiyako. Ko iyemaeŇčge bigi emunjoruko iya inako e buruburu nuwaiya vowo thovuye moli iya i kivwala thetheghan…®ko vowoniye.
\v 24 Krais mava i ru e Ňčgolo boboma ghar…®ghar…® va th…® vatad e n…®manji, iya emunjoruko Ňčgal…®Ňčgal…®ya. Iye va veru e buruburu moli t…®ne na e mbaŇčake iyake i yomara Loi e marae ghinda kaiwanda.
\p 
\v 25 Krais va ve ru e buruburu, ko iyemaeŇčge ma vambe ve ravowovowo eŇčge ghamberegha Ňčgoreiya Jiu lenji ravowovowo lagh…®ye theghathegha regha na regha i th…®na thetheghan mad…®bae na ve ru e Woluwolu Boboma Moliko t…®ne.
\v 26 Kaiwae thoŇčgo mbe i rovowovowo eŇčge ghamberegha, mbene i ghataghataŇča eŇčge v…®r…®, i ri mbaŇčaniye Loi va i vakatha yambaneke. IyemaeŇčge ma Ňčgoreiye. MbaŇčake iyake mbaŇča le ghambako i ghenetha, na amalagh…®niye va i yomara mbe mbaŇčara eŇčge mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye kaiwae, na mbe ghamberegha vara le mare e t…®ne, i rakayathu thar…®.
\v 27 Na reghava, lolo regha na regha mbene mbaŇčara eŇčge i mare, na e ghereiye ve kot.
\v 28 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva Krais vambe ghamberegha vara i vatomwe na i mare Ňčgoreiya vowo ghar…®ghar…® lemoyo lenji thar…®. Na tembene i yomarava mbaŇčaiwoniye, ma Ňčgoreiya ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® ghavanamwe kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge thavala th…® roroghagha amalagh…®niye kaiwae ne i vamoruŇčgi.\fig Woluwolu Boboma Moliko ina e Ňägolo Boboma e t…®ne|alt="most holy place" src="bk00278c.tif" size="span" copy="BFBS (Knowles-Bass)" ref="9:25"\fig*
\c 10
\s1 Krais va i mare mbaŇčara na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye kaiwae
\p 
\v 1 Kaiwae Mosese le Mbaro iye thovuyeko iya amba i menamenako mbema ŇčgaliŇčgaliya eŇčge, na iye ghathuwathuwa amba ma Ňčgoreiya thovuyeko moli. Iya kaiwae Mbaro ma val…®kaiwae i vanamweŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® mena th…® kurukururu na th…® rumwaru, othembe theghathegha regha na regha th…® vakavakatha vowo.
\v 2 ThoŇčgo mbema emunjoru ghar…®ghar…®ko va th…® kurukururu weya Loi th…® vowo mbaŇčarako na kaero i thavwiyathu lenji thar…®, mbala tembe ma th…® rerenuwaŇčava e gharenjiko thiye th…® thar…®, iyako mbala i vakatha th…® viyathu vowo ghavakatha.
\v 3 Ko iyemaeŇčge vowoko iya th…® vakavakatha theghathegha regha na reghako i vavanuwov…®r…® weŇčgi thiye thar…® gharavakathaŇčgi.
\v 4 Kaiwae burumwaka gh…®mogh…®moru na gout mad…®banji ma val…®kaiwae i rakayathu ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®.
\p 
\v 5 Iya kaiwae, mbaŇča Krais kaero ghambaŇča i njama e yambaneke, i dage weya Loi iŇča:
\q1 Thetheghan ghanjivowovowo ma nuwana nuwaiya, ko iyemaeŇčge va u vivatharaweya riwaŇčguke u woveŇčgo ya vakaiwoŇča kaiwan.
\q1 
\v 6 Th…® Ňčambwa vowo na thar…® vowoniye ma u warariŇča.
\q1 
\v 7 Ko amba ghino yaŇča, ‚ÄúO Loi, ghinoke, ya mena na ya vakatha len renuwaŇčana, Ňčgoreiya kaerova th…® rorinjoŇča Buk Boboma e t…®ne.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 10:7 \xt Sam 40:6-8\x*
\m 
\v 8 (Mbaro i woraŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakathaŇčgiya vowoko thiyako.) E rororiko iyako t…®ne, iviva iŇča, ‚ÄúThetheghan vowoniye, th…® Ňčambwa vowo, na thar…® vowoniye ma nuwaniya na ma u warariŇča.‚ÄĚ
\v 9 Ko amba iŇča, ‚ÄúGhinoke, ya mena na ya vakatha len renuwaŇčana.‚ÄĚ Iya kaiwae kamwath…®ma i vivama kaero i rakayathu na kaero i vamidiya kamwath…® theghewoniye.
\v 10 Kaiwae Jisas Krais kaerova i mena na i vamboromboro Loi le renuwaŇča, i wogiya ghamberegha riwae na i vowo mbaŇčara na mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye kaiwae, i vabobomainda.
\p 
\v 11 MbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ravowovowo regha na regha th…® ndeghath…® na th…® vakavakatha kururu kaiwoniye na mbaŇčathaŇčar…® th…® vowo vovwatha mbe vowo regha eŇčge, ko iyemaeŇčge vowoko iyako ma val…®kaiwae i thavwiyathu thar…®.
\v 12 IyemaeŇčge Krais vambe i vakatha eŇčge vowo regha ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® kaiwae, na vowoko iyako ele vur…®gheghe mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako, ko amba i yaku Loi ele val…®vaŇčga e uneko.
\v 13 MbaŇčake mbe inawe i roroghagha ghaghad Loi i biginjoŇčaŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®ya e gheghe raberabe.
\v 14 Val…®kaiwae i roroghagha Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae vowo vambe regha eŇčge vara i vakatha, na ghinda thavala kaero i vabobomainda, kaero i vanamwe wagiyaweinda na ra rumwaru e marae mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\p 
\v 15 Nyao Boboma tembe i utuŇčava weinda iya utuutuke iyake. I viva iŇča:
\q1 
\v 16 Giya iŇča, ‚ÄúMbaŇča muyaiko ne ya vakatha dagerawe kaiwanji Ňčgoreiyake. Ne ya woraweya lo mbaro e gharenji na th…® ghareghare, na ya rori e lenji renuwaŇčako na th…® ghambu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 10:16 \xt Jer 31:33\x*
\q1 
\v 17 Na mbowo i gotubweva iŇča, ‚ÄúLenji thar…® na lenji vakatha raraithar…® mane tembe ya renuwaŇčakikiva.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 10:17 \xt Jer 31:34\x*
\m 
\v 18 Iya kaiwae, mbaŇča Loi kaero i numotena ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…®, ma tembe val…®kaiwaeva ravowovowo i vakathava vowo thar…® kaiwae.
\s1 Utu vavur…®gheghe ghataŇčaghath…® kaiwae
\p 
\v 19 Iya kaiwae, lo bodaboda, Jisas Krais mad…®bae kaiwae val…®kaiwae weinda la gharematuwo ra ru e Woluwolu Bobomako Moli t…®ne Loi e marae.
\v 20 Jisas kaero i vugh…® weinda ghamba ruruko ghakamwath…® togha. Iye yawal…® ghakamwath…®, na kwamako iyava th…® livakwate na i gana Woluwolu Bobomako Moli ghaghamba ruwe mbaŇčake kaero i mavu. Va i mavu Jisas e riwae na i mare kaiwanda.
\v 21 La ravowovowo lagh…®ye kaero inawe, iye i njimbukikiya Loi le Ňčgolo.
\v 22 Wo ra wa weya Loi ghadidiye e gharendake th…® emunjoru na wonjowe ma inawe na la loŇčweghath…® mbe i vur…®gheghe. Ra wawe kaiwae kaero i vanamwe gharenda na la thar…® mbigh…®wae iko, na kaero i thavwiya riwanda e mbwa thovuye.
\v 23 Wo ra vatada la loŇčweghath…®ke lagh…®ye weya Loi na ra vikikighath…® kaiwae ra ghareghare nevole i giya thovuye weinda kaero ra utuŇčaŇčgi, kaiwae ra vareminja Loi ne i vamboromboro Ňčgoreiya le dageraweko.
\v 24 Na wo ra rerenuwaŇča na ra vevavur…®ghegheŇčainda na ra vegharethovuinda na ra vakatha vakatha thovuye.
\v 25 Thava ra viyathu mevathavatha thanavuniye, Ňčgoreiya vavana th…® vakavakatha. IyemaeŇčge ra veutu vavur…®gheghe weinda na ra vakatha mbela iyako kaiwae Giya le njoghama kaero i gheneghenetha.
\p 
\v 26 ThoŇčgo kaero ra ghareghareya totoko iya emunjoruko ko iyemaeŇčge mbema nuwandake nuwaiya ra vakavakathava thar…®, ma tembe vowo reghava inawe na ne i thavwiyathu la thar…®.
\v 27 IyemaeŇčge mbema weinda eŇčge la mararu na ra roroghagha Loi ne i vanivaŇčainda na i vaŇčguraweinda e nd…®gheko dayaghawaeko lagh…®ye e t…®ne, iya Loi ne i ŇčambuŇčgiya ghath…®gh…®yakowe.
\v 28 Thelolo regha i botewo Mosese le Mbaro na ragovambwara theghewo o thegheto, ghalith…® mbe mare eŇčge, mane gharenji i njawe.
\v 29 Ko iyemaeŇčge thoŇčgo lolo regha i wonjoŇčanjoŇča Jisas na iŇča, ‚ÄúIye ma Loi Nariye Ňčgoreiye,‚ÄĚ o thoŇčgo i wovanasinasiyeŇča madibeko iya i vaemunjoruŇča dageraweko togha na i thavwiyathu la thar…®ko, o thoŇčgo lolo regha i utuvathar…® weya Nyao Gharegharethovuniye, loloko iyako ghalith…® ne i lagh…®ye moli i kivwala loloko i botewo Mosese le Mbaroko ghalith…®.
\v 30 Kaiwae ra ghareghare Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúGhino womberegha ya liya thoru na ya lith…® weŇčga lemi vakathana raithar…® modae.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 10:30 \xt Mba 32:35; Mba 32:36; Sam 135:14\x* Na tembe iŇčava, ‚ÄúGiya ne i ghathaŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…®.‚ÄĚ
\v 31 Ghamba mararu lagh…®ye moli thoŇčgo Loi e yawayawaliye i laweghath…®inda lith…® kaiwae.
\p 
\v 32 Wo hu renuwaŇčanjogha mbaŇča me vivako, va ŇčgoroŇčga ghemi, mbaŇčaniye Toto Thovuye manjamanjalaniye i woya weŇčga. Vuyowo lemoyo va th…® ghan…®njoŇčanjoŇčaŇčga na hu vaidiya v…®r…®niye, iyemaeŇčge hu ghataŇčaghath…® na hu ndeghath…® vur…®gheghe.
\v 33 MbaŇča vavana va th…® vandeghath…®Ňčga wabwi e maranji amba th…® utuvathar…® e ghemi na th…® vakatha vathar…® weŇčga. Na mbaŇča vavana hu ndevaŇčga weŇčgiya ghamune th…® vakatha Ňčgorake weŇčgi na hu thalavuŇčgi.
\v 34 MbaŇča thoŇčgo va th…® vaŇčguruwoŇčgiya ghamune vavana e thiyo, gharemi i njaweŇčgi na hu vakatha ghanjithalavu. MbaŇča rambarombaro va th…® mban bwagabwaga lemi bigibigi, hu warari, kaiwae hu ghareghare vwenyevwenye moli mbe ina weŇčga, iya i meghabanako.
\p 
\v 35 Iya kaiwae thava hu ndeiteta lemi gharematuwona, kaiwae iyana ne i womena modami lagh…®ye,
\v 36 na wo hu ghataŇčaghath…® na hu vakatha Loi le renuwaŇča na budakaiya le dagerawe hu wo e ghemi.
\q1 
\v 37 Kaiwae mbaŇča nasiye moli, iya thela i menamenako i vutha mane i vuyowo.
\q1 
\v 38 Ko iyemaeŇčge lo ghar…®ghar…®ko iya th…® rumwaruko, ne e yawayawalinji kaiwae th…® loŇčweghath…®, na thoŇčgo regha i njogha e ghereiye, mane ya warari kaiwae.\x - \xo 10:38 \xt Hab 2:3,4\x*
\m 
\v 39 Ko iyemaeŇčge ghinda ma ghar…®ghar…® th…® ndendenjogha e ghereinji na th…® mukuwoŇčgi, iyemaeŇčge ghinda kaero ra loŇčweghath…® na ra vaidiya vamoru.
\c 11
\s1 LoŇčweghath…® utuutuniye
\p 
\v 1 LoŇčweghath…® gharerenuwaŇča Ňčgoreiyake. Ra ghareghare wagiyawe emunjoru thovuyeko iya ra roroghagha kaiwaeko ne ra vaidi. Othembe ma ra thuwe e marandake, iyemaeŇčge ra ghareghare wagiyawe mbe inawe.
\v 2 Ghar…®ghar…® me vivako lenji loŇčweghath…® kaiwae Loi i wovathovuthovuyeŇčaŇčgi.
\p 
\v 3 La loŇčweghath…® e t…®ne ra ghareghare Loi va i vakatha yambaneke na buruburu e ghal…®Ňčae, iya kaiwae budakaiya ra thuwe e marandake Loi va i vakatha e thebigiya ma ra thuwe.
\p 
\v 4 LoŇčweghath…® e t…®ne Eibol i vakatha vowo thovuye i voro weya Loi na iyako i thovuye kivwala Kein le vowo. Le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae Loi i warariŇča na i wovarumwarumwaruŇča, kaiwae Loi mbe ghamberegha i wovarumwarumwaruŇča le vowoko. Le vareminjeko kaiwae othembe kaero i mare, iyemaeŇčge le loŇčweghath…®ko i vavur…®ghegheŇčainda.
\p 
\v 5 Inok le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae Loi mbe i vaŇčgu vara bwanabwana, mava i mare. Mava th…® vaidi muna riwae kaiwae Loi vama i yovaŇčgu, na amba muyai i yovaŇčgu. Buk Boboma iŇča Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúYa warari Inok kaiwae.‚ÄĚ
\v 6 ThoŇčgo ma e la loŇčweghath…® Loi mane i warari kaiwanda. Kaiwae thela thoŇčgo nuwaiya i mena weya Loi, wo i loŇčweghath…® Loi inawe na Loi i giya modae thovuye weŇčgiya thavala th…® tamwe.
\p 
\v 7 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Nowa i vandeŇče na i wovatha Loi ghal…®Ňčae, mbaŇča va i vanuwov…®r…® bigibigiko ne th…® yomara e ghamwaeko kaiwanji, iya amba ma val…®kaiwae i thuweko. Kaiwae Loi ghayavwatata i lagh…®ye weya Nowa, i ghambugha Loi le renuwaŇčako na i vatada waŇčga amalagh…®niye na le ŇčgaŇčga th…® vaidiya vamoruwe. Nowa le vakathako i woraŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® e mbaŇčako iyako raraithar…®Ňčgi, na kaiwae amalagh…®niye i loŇčweghath…® Loi iŇča, ‚ÄúNowa iye lolo rumwarumwaruniye.‚ÄĚ
\p 
\v 8 Eibraham le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae i vakatha i ghambugha Loi le renuwaŇča mbaŇča i kularaŇčgiya e ghambae na i wa e vanautuma regha Loi i dagerawewe na i vatomwewe, othembe mava i ghareghare the val…®vaŇčga i reŇčakowe.
\v 9 Le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae i mebobwari dagerawe ghembaniye e t…®ne, i ghenaghena e yaŇčavaŇčgavaŇčga t…®ne. Aisake na Jeikob vambe th…® yakuyakuva Ňčgoreiyako na Loi tembe i dageraweva weŇčgi na th…® yakuŇča val…®vaŇčgako iyako.
\v 10 Eibraham i mebobwari gheko kaiwae va nuwaiya moli wone i yaku e ghemba ghambagh…®mbagh…® memeghabananiye, iya Loi i renuwaŇčako na i vatad.
\p 
\v 11 Eibraham le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae i vakatha Loi le vur…®gheghe e t…®ne th…® vaidiya Ňčgama othembe amalagh…®niye vama i amalagh…®sar…® na levo Sera i kwama. Amalagh…®niye va i vareminja Loi val…®kaiwae i vamboromboro le dageraweko.
\v 12 Othembe vama i amalagh…®sar…® moli na kaero i rovala, amalagh…®niye ghamberegha e mad…®bae, orumburumbuye lemoyo moli, lenji ghanaghanagha Ňčgoreiya gh…®tara e buruburuko na kerakera e njigh…®ko ghadidiye ma val…®kaiwae ra vaona.
\p 
\v 13 Ghar…®ghar…®ko wolagh…®ye thiyako vambe th…® loŇčgaloŇčga vara loŇčweghath…® e t…®ne ghaghad veth…® mare. Bigibigiko Loi va i dageraweko kaiwanji mava regha mun i vaidi, ko iyemaeŇčge th…® gh…®maraghaoko e ghamwanjiko i bwagabwaga moli weŇčgi na th…® warariŇča ne i yomara Ňčgoreiye. Mava th…® monjinaŇča na th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúGhime bobwari na ra loŇčga bwagabwaga e yambaneke.‚ÄĚ
\v 14 Ghar…®ghar…® iya th…® utuŇča Ňčgoreiyako i woraŇčgiya thiye th…® tamwetamweya vanautuma ne th…® wo na ghambanji moli.
\v 15 ThoŇčgo va th…® rerenuwaŇča vanautumako va th…® iteteko kaiwae, mbala kaerova th…® raka njogha.
\v 16 IyemaeŇčge vanautuma thovuye moli gharerenuwaŇča mbe ina vara weŇčgi, iye buruburu ghembaniye. Iya kaiwae Loi ma i monjina na thoŇčgo th…®Ňča iye lenji Loi, kaiwae kaero i vivatharaweya ghemba kaiwanji.
\p 
\v 17-18 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Eibraham i vatomweya nariye Aisake vowo kaiwae, mbaŇča Loi i mando. Loi va i dagerawewe na iŇča, ‚ÄúWeya naru Aisake nevole orumburumbu th…® yomara‚ÄĚ,\x - \xo 11:17-18 \xt R…®gh 21:12\x* iyemaeŇčge va i vatomweyathu moliya nariye mbe reghaeŇčge vowo kaiwae.
\v 19 Eibraham va i ghareghare Loi val…®kaiwae i vakatha Aisake na i thuweiru mare e t…®ne na tembe e yawayawaliyeva. Na val…®kaiwae raŇča mbaŇča Loi i dagetena Eibraham na thava i vakowana Aisake yawaliye, iyako Ňčgoreiya Eibraham i vaŇčgunjogha nariye mare e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 20 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Aisake i giya le ŇčgaŇčga, Jeikob na Iso ghanjidagemwaewo mbaŇča i menamenako kaiwae.
\p 
\v 21 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae, mbaŇča Jeikob le mare vama evasiwae, i giya Josep le ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru theghewo ghanjidagemwaewo mbaŇča i menamenako kaiwae. Na vama i woeŇčge le pwasike, i ndevadede ghamba v…®ghath…®ko kaero i kururu weya Loi.
\p 
\v 22 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae, mbaŇča Josep le mare vama i gheneghenetha, iŇča, ‚ÄúNevole mbaŇča regha amba wabwi Isirel th…® raka raŇčgi Ijipt,‚ÄĚ na i giya ghanjimbaro nevole e mbaŇčako iyako th…® mbana wokiwokiyeko na th…® raka raŇčgi.
\p 
\v 23 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Mosese t…®nae na ramae weinji lenji gharematuwo th…® raka kiŇč…®ko le mbaro na narinjiko le vir…® e ghereiye th…® wothuwele e Ňčgolo t…®ne manjala umboto e t…®ne, kaiwae Ňčgamako ghayamoyamo va i thovuye moli.
\p 
\v 24 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae i vakatha Mosese, mbaŇča vama i lagh…®ye mava nuwaiya ghar…®ghar…® th…®Ňča amalagh…®niye kiŇč…®ko yawarumbuye nariye.
\v 25 Va i renuwaŇča nuwaiya weiyaŇčgiya Loi le ghar…®ghar…® wo th…® ghataŇča v…®r…®, na thava i warariŇča thar…® thanavuniye ghawarari, iya ma ghambaŇčako molao i vawarariŇča.
\v 26 I renuwaŇča na i dagewe ghamberegha, ‚ÄúI thovuye eŇčge Mesaiya kaiwae na ghar…®ghar…® th…® utuvathar…® weŇčgo, na i thar…® eŇčge Ijipt vwenyevwenyeniye ya vwenyevwenyewe.‚ÄĚ Va i renuwaŇča Ňčgoreiyako kaiwae e marae vambe i vonjimbughath…® vara modoko iya Loi ne i giyakowe.
\p 
\v 27 Le loŇčweghath…® kaiwae Mosese i iteta Ijipt, mava weiye mun le mararu othembe kiŇč…®ko thoŇčgo i gaith…®. RaŇčaeŇčge vama i thuweya Loi iya ma ra thuwe e marandake iya kaiwae i rombeleŇčge.
\v 28 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae i vakatha Thaga ValaŇčani na i vauna sip mad…®bae e mbwaŇčaŇčgilako vwatanji na ghaumbwaumbwa vaŇčga na vaŇčga, na mbala thava Mareko gha Nyao i gaboŇčgiya Isirel lenji ŇčgaŇčga gh…®mogh…®moru vir…® vivaŇčgi.
\p 
\v 29 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Isirel th…® rakalawa e Njigh…® Sosoro Ňčgoreiye th…® rakalawa e maŇčgo; ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča Ijipt th…® mando na th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiya Isirel meth…® vakathako, njigh…®ko i wovululuŇčgi na thiya munumare.
\p 
\v 30 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae Isirel th…® vagh…®liya Jeriko ghagana mbaŇča regha na regha na ghepir…®ninji e t…®ne ganako i mav…®r…®.
\p 
\v 31 LoŇčweghath…® kaiwae i vakatha Reihab, iye wevo i mbana riwae modae, mava i mare weiyaŇčgiya Jeriko ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® goriwoyathu iya Loi va i mukuwoŇčgiko, kaiwae va i vaŇčguruwoŇčgiya Isirel rakelakela theghewo ele Ňčgolo na i thalavuŇčgi.
\p 
\v 32 Wone ya utuŇčava the utuutu? Ma mbaŇča i vatomwe na val…®kaiwae ya utuŇča Gidiyon, Barak, Samson, Jepta,\f + \fr 11:32 \ft Va i vivako Barak iye va Jiu ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji randeviva regha. Iye i viva e lenji gaith…® na th…® vakatha ghanjith…®gh…®ya na th…® dobu (Ragh 4 na 5). Jepta va ragagaith…® lagh…®ye moli. Va mbaŇča regha iye Israel ghar…®ghar…®niye lenji randeviva.\f* Deivid, Samuwel na ghal…®Ňčae gharautu utuutuninji e ghemi.
\v 33 Lenji loŇčweghath…® kaiwae vavana th…® gaith…® weŇčgiya vanautuma vavana na th…® kivwalaŇčgi, vavana th…® mbaroŇča na thovuyeŇčgiya ghembaghemba, vavana th…® vaidiya Loi le dagerawe une, vavana th…® vigana laiyon ghae,
\v 34 vavana nd…®ghe le vur…®gheghe ma bolae ina e riwanji, vavana ghanjith…®gh…®yako iya nuwanjiya th…® gaboŇčgi e gaith…®ko ghaghalith…® th…® voiteteŇčgi, vavana lenji njavovo e t…®ne th…® vaidiya vur…®gheghe, vavana gaith…® e t…®ne th…® vur…®gheghe moli na th…® kivwalaŇčgiya val…®vaŇčga regha lenji ragagaith…® na th…® vonjogha.
\v 35 Wanakau vavana lenji bodaboda vavana th…® thuweiru mare e t…®ne na th…® vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgi. Ko iyemaeŇčge ghar…®ghar…® vavana ghanjith…®gh…®ya th…® tagavotagamena weŇčgi na th…® mare. Na othembe ghanjith…®gh…®yako th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo hu ndeghereiyewana Loi ne wo rakayathuŇčga,‚ÄĚ iyemaeŇčge th…® botewoyathu, kaiwae nuwanjiya thuweiruva na th…® wo yawal…®ko memeghabananiyeko.
\v 36 Vavana ghar…®ghar…® th…® vav…®r…®Ňčgi na th…® liya thiyo vur…®gheghe th…® yab…®b…®Ňčgiwe; vavana ghar…®ghar…® th…® Ňčgar…®Ňčgi e sen na th…® vaŇčguruwoŇčgi e thiyo.
\v 37 Vavana ghar…®ghar…® th…® tagavavamareŇčgi e var…®; vavana th…® sowo ten…®Ňčgi na vavana th…® govamareŇčgi e gaith…® ghaghalith…®. Vavana mbema th…® rakaraka loloŇčga eŇčge, th…® njimbo sip na gout njimwanji, th…® tabo mbinyembinyeŇčgu, th…® vakavakatha v…®r…® weŇčgi na ma th…® ghana ghanjighar…®.
\v 38 Va th…® vovo loloŇčga e vur…®vur…® vwatavwata e val…®vaŇčga ma mbwaniye, e ououko vwatavwatanji na th…® ghenaghena e maŇčgavar…® na e ther…®mbun. Yambaneke ghar…®ghar…®niye th…® vakatha vathar…® weŇčgiya raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko thiyako na th…® woraŇčgiya thiye ma e lenji thovuye na val…®kaiwae th…® yaku na regha weinjiyaŇčgi.
\p 
\v 39 Ghar…®ghar…®ke vara wolagh…®ye thiyake lenji loŇčweghath…® kaiwae Loi i wovathovuthovuyeŇčaŇčgi. IyemaeŇčge thovuyeko iya Loi va i dageraweko mava th…® vaidi,
\v 40 kaiwae Loi va i renuwaŇča wo i woraweya thovuyeko moli kaiwanda. Mava nuwaiya thiye wo th…® thovuyekai, ko iyemaeŇčge nuwaiya thiya na ghinda ra rumwaru na regha.
\c 12
\s1 Loi iye ramanda na ghandaravathanavu thovuye
\p 
\v 1 Iya kaiwae raloŇčweloŇčweghath…®ko thiyako thiye Ňčgoranjiya wabwi lagh…®ye th…® rovagh…®liyainda na th…® ghewainda, val…®kaiwae weinda la ghataŇčaghath…® wo ra ruku loŇčweghath…® e ghakamwath…® na i ghembeya ghamwandako. Bigibigiko wolagh…®ye iya i ganeindake na ma val…®kaiwanda ra rukuna thovuye, weiye thar…® thanavuniye i laweghath…®inda ra bigiyathu.
\v 2 Na marandake mbe ra vonjimbughath…® vara Jisas, iye la loŇčweghath…®ke r…®ghethoru na gharavanamwe. Iye va i ghataŇčaghath…®gha kros v…®r…®niye na mava i rerenuwaŇča monjinaniye, kaiwae i ghareghare warari lagh…®ye mbe ina e ghamwaeko tene ve vaidi. Na e mbaŇčake iyake i yaku Loi ele ghamba yaku vwenyevwenye t…®ne val…®vaŇčga e uneko.
\v 3 Wo hu renuwaŇča vuyowoko va i ruwoko, Jisas, amalagh…®niye va i ghataŇčaghath…® ghathar…® gharavakatha lenji vakatha vathar…®we, iya kaiwae ghemi thava hu gharelagh…®lagh…® na hu viyathu lemi ghamba ndeghath…®na.
\p 
\v 4 Kaiwae ghemi mbe inamiwe hu rorovur…®gheghe weimi thar…® thanavuniye na ghar…®ghar…® th…® th…®gh…®yawanaŇčga, ko iyemaeŇčge ghemina regha amba ma i mare.
\v 5 Tha huya njavovo na kaero hu renuwaŇča vaghalawa ghamiutu vavur…®gheghe iyava th…® rori e Buk Bobomako t…®ne? I dage weŇčgiya le ŇčgaŇčga Ňčgoreiyake,
\q1 NaruŇčgu, thoŇčgo Giya i vathanavuŇčge, thava u utu na uŇča ma e uneune, na thoŇčgo i govambwara len thar…®, thava len rovur…®gheghena i thalat…®vawe.
\q1 
\v 6 Kaiwae Giya ghar…®ghar…®ko iya i gharethovuko weŇčgi i vathanavuŇčgi, na ghar…®ghar…®ko iya ghareko weŇčgi Ňčgoreiya le ŇčgaŇčga, i vatomweya kamwath…® weŇčgi.\x - \xo 12:6 \xt Vav 3:11,12\x*
\p 
\v 7 Mbe hu ghataŇčaghath…®gha v…®r…®na hu vavaidina, kaiwae e t…®ne Loi i vathanavuŇčga. I vakatha Ňčgoreiyako weŇčga kaiwae ghemi Ňčgoreiya le ŇčgaŇčga. Thare Ňčgama regha inawe na ramae mane i vathanavu? (Nandere.)
\v 8 Loi le ŇčgaŇčgake wolagh…®ye i vathanavuŇčgi. ThoŇčgo ma i vavathanavuŇčga, gharerenuwaŇča Ňčgoreiye ghemi ma le ŇčgaŇčga moli Ňčgoreiye, ko iyemaeŇčge ghemi Ňčgoreiya kamwath…® gamagainiye.
\v 9 Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, oramanda e yambaneke mbe th…® vavathanavuindava na ra yavwatatawanaŇčgi. Iya kaiwae mbala ra vatomweinda emunjoru weya Ramanda e buruburu le vavathanavuko iya i giya ko weinda na ra vaidiya yawalinda.
\v 10 Oramanda mbe mbaŇča ubotu eŇčge th…® vathanavuinda; ko iyemaeŇčge Loi i vathanavuinda la thovuye kaiwae, nuwaiya ra boboma Ňčgoreiya amalagh…®niye i boboma.
\v 11 MbaŇča ra vavaidiya vathanavu, e mbaŇčako iyako gham…®nanda i thar…®, gham…®nanda ma i warawarari. Ko iyemaeŇčge mbaŇča muyai amba ra thuweya une ve raŇčgi thavala Loi i vavathanavu weŇčgi i vanamweŇčgi na ghanjithanavu i rumwaru na lenji yakuyaku tembe Ňčgoreiyeva.
\p 
\v 12 Thava hu njavovo. IyemaeŇčge hu vavur…®ghegheva lemi loŇčweghath…®,
\v 13 na mbe hu ghao e ghamwamina. ThoŇčgo ne hu vakatha Ňčgoreiyako, iya ghamunena iya lenji loŇčweghath…® i njavovo mane th…® thar…® moli, ko iyemaeŇčge ne th…® vaidiva lenji vur…®gheghe.
\s1 Vavathanavu na vavur…®gheghe
\p 
\v 14 Hu mando na lemi yakuyaku i thovuye weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye weiye gharemal…®l…®. Na hu mando hu rovur…®ghegheŇča thanavu thovuye moli ghavakatha. Kaiwae thoŇčgo ghandathanavu ma i rumwaru mane val…®kaiwanda ra thuweya Giya.
\v 15 Hu njimbukikiŇčga na thava ghemina regha i ndeiteta Loi le mwaewo bwagabwaga. Na tembe Ňčgoreiyeva thava ghemina regha i vakatha thar…® weŇčgiya ghaune, iwaeŇčge ne Ňčgoreiye watheliliye iya i mbuthu na lagh…®ye moli, na ele ghambako tembe raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® i ghanagha ne th…® vakathava thar…® na th…® mbigh…® Loi e marae.
\v 16 Hu njimbukikiŇčga na thava ghemina regha i vakavakatha yathima thanavuniye. Na thava ghemina regha i vakatha Ňčgoreiya Iso, iye mava Loi gharerenuwaŇča inawe, va mbe ghan…®Ňčgama mbaŇčara eŇčge kaiwae i giyayathu vir…®viva ghabebe mbalava i mena weya ramae.
\v 17 Na kaero hu ghareghare va mbaŇča regha nuwaiya i wo dage mwaewo weya ramae mbaŇča i menamenako kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge ramae i vaghareghareya dage mwaewoko iyako. Othembe Iso va i raŇči vwayata dageraweko iyako kaiwae, iyemaeŇčge ramae mava val…®kaiwae i v…®va le renuwaŇča.
\p 
\v 18 Hu njimbukikiŇčga Ňčgoreiyako, kaiwae iya ghinda ra vaidike ma Ňčgoreiya thiye me vivako meth…® vaidi. Wabwi Isirel va th…® mena th…® vutha e yambaneke ouniye Sainai amba th…® thuweya nd…®ghe i rara, Ňčgal…®l…® i poku na i vakatha i momouwo na i rovir…®,
\v 19 na th…® loŇčweya mema ghal…®Ňčae lagh…®ye. Na tembe th…® loŇčweva Loi ghal…®Ňčae, i vakatha th…® mararu lagh…®ye na th…® dage weya Mosese th…®Ňča, ‚ÄúThava tembe i utuutuva weime na wo loŇčweya ghal…®Ňčae.‚ÄĚ
\v 20 Kaiwae mava nuwanjiya ghal…®Ňčaeko iyava iŇčako, ‚ÄúThoŇčgo lolo o thoŇčgo thetheghan regha i vur…®ghath…®gha ouke iyake ne th…® tagavamare e var…®.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:20 \xt RaŇč 19:12,13\x*
\v 21 Bigiko iyava th…® thuweko ghayamoyamo i maramararu moli iya kaiwae Mosese iŇča, ‚ÄúMararu kaiwae ya tage.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:21 \xt Mba 9:19\x*
\p 
\v 22 IyemaeŇčge ghinda kaero ra vutha e Ou Saiyon, iye Jerusalem, ina e buruburu, iye Loi e yawayawaliye ghambae. Kaero ra thuweŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, mbunja alalamaŇčgo th…® mevathavatha na th…® warawarari.
\v 23 Kaero ra mena ra tubwe ekelesiya e t…®ne na Ňčgoranda Loi nariye gamau, na i rorinjoŇča idanda e buk t…®ne e buruburu. Kaero ra mena weya Loi iye ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye ghanjiragatha. Na ra mena ra tubwe weŇčgiya ghar…®ghar…® rumwarumwaru mevivako, thavala kaerova th…® mare na Loi i vanamweŇčgi na th…® rumwaru.
\v 24 Kaero ra mena weya Jisas, iye va i vamidiya dagerawe togha ghar…®ghar…® na Loi e ghanjilughawoghawo, na mad…®bae i voru i vaemunjoruŇča dageraweko togha iyako. Eibol mad…®bae va i dobu e thelauko vwatae i woraŇčgiya gharagagaith…® ne e ghalith…®, ko iyemaeŇčge Jisas mad…®bae va i voru i woraŇčgiya Loi i numotena la thar…®.
\p 
\v 25 Hu njimbukikiŇčga na thava hu botewotho Loi le utuutuko weŇčga. Thavala mevivako meth…® botewo utu vur…®ghegheniye, iya lolo va i dage weŇčgi e yambaneke, mava th…® voiteta ghanjilith…®ko. E mbaŇčake iyake Loi i giya utu vur…®ghegheniye i njama e buruburu, na thoŇčgo ra wogiya ghereindawe, ne ŇčgoroŇčga raŇča na ra voiteta lith…®ko iyako?
\v 26 Va e mbaŇčako iyako i utu na le utuko i vakatha mbarimbariri e yambaneke ko iyemaeŇčge e mbaŇčake iyake kaerova i dagerawe iŇča, ‚ÄúMbowone mbaŇčarava ya vandindiŇčgiya yambane na buruburu.‚ÄĚ\x - \xo 12:26 \xt Hag 2:6\x*
\v 27 Na mbowo iŇčava, ‚ÄúMbowo mbaŇčarava‚ÄĚ i woraŇčgiya emunjoru bigibigike thiyake mbowone th…® mbarimbaririva ‚ÄĒ thiye iyava Loi i vakathaŇčgiko na ra thuwe e marandake ‚ÄĒ ne th…®ko. IyaŇčganiya ma val…®kaiwae i mbarimbariri th…® meghabana.
\p 
\v 28 Ghinda kaero ra wo ghamba mbaroko iya ma val…®kaiwae i mbarimbaririko, iya kaiwae weinda la vata agowe ra kururu weya Loi Ňčgoreiya amalagh…®niye i warariŇčako. Ra kururu weinda la yavwatata na la mararu,
\v 29 kaiwae la Loi iye Ňčgoreiya nd…®ghe val…®kaiwaya i Ňčambuyathu bigibigike wolagh…®ye.\x - \xo 12:29 \xt Mba 4:24\x*
\c 13
\s1 Utu vavur…®gheghe vavana
\p 
\v 1 Gharethovu thanavuniye hu vakatha valaŇča weŇčgiya lemi val…®raloŇčweloŇčweghath…® Ňčgoreiya thiye lemi bodaboda.
\v 2 Ne hu nderenuwaŇča valawe mbe hu kula vathaŇčgiya bobwari e lemi ŇčgoloŇčgolona. Vavana va th…® vakatha Ňčgoreiyako na th…® kula vathaŇčgiya nyao thovuthovuye, ko iyemaeŇčge mava th…® ghareghare thela i wo nyao thovuthovuye iya th…® kula vathaŇčgina.
\v 3 Hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgiya ghamune inanji e thiyo hu vakatha thalavu weŇčgi na ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya ghemi inami e thiyo weimiyaŇčgi. Na Ňčgoreiya ghamune th…® ghataŇča v…®r…®, hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgi na ghayamoyamo Ňčgoreiya ghemi tembe hu vaidiva iya v…®r…®ko iyako.
\p 
\v 4 Ghe iye bigi lagh…®ye moli, iya kaiwae ghar…®ghar…®ke wolagh…®ye val…®kaiwae th…® yavwatatawana. Ghemi ragheghe lemi ghe mbe i th…®na na thava yathima thanavuniye i vambigh…®ya. Thavala th…® vakatha yathima thanavuniye Loi ne ve ghathaŇčgi.
\v 5 Mani ghagharethovu thava i Ňčgara yawalimina ghaloŇčgaloŇčga, ko iyemaeŇčge the bigiya inawe hu vaidi mbema hu warariŇča eŇčge. Kaiwae Loi kaerova i utuvao weinda ghanjimbukikiŇčga iŇča;
\q1 Ma mbaŇča regha ya iteteŇčga, ma mbaŇča regha ya ghene viyathuŇčga.\x - \xo 13:5 \xt Mba 31:6\x*
\m 
\v 6 Iya kaiwae val…®kaiwae weinda la gharematuwo raŇča;
\q1 Giya iye wo Rathalavu,
\q1 iya kaiwae mane ya mararu.
\q1 Ma ya rerenuwaŇča budakaiya thoŇčgo ghar…®ghar…® th…® vakatha e ghino.\x - \xo 13:6 \xt Sam 118:6,7\x*
\p 
\v 7 Hu renuwaŇčakikiŇčgiya thavala va th…® ndeviva ekelesiyana e t…®ne, thiye va th…® utuŇča Loi ghal…®Ňčae weŇčga. Yawalinji ghaloŇčgaloŇčga na lenji loŇčweghath…® une wo hu renuwaŇčaŇčgi, na mbala ghemi lemi loŇčweghath…®na Ňčgoreiya thiye lenji loŇčweghath…®.
\v 8 Jisas Krais mbe reghaeŇčge vara, menda, noroke na mbaŇčako wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako.
\p 
\v 9 Thava vavaghare mbe tomethi na tomethi th…® wo nuwami na hu roiteta emunjoruna. Ko iyemaeŇčge hu vatomweŇčga eŇčge Loi ele mwaewo bwagabwagana iya ne i vavur…®ghegha yawalimina. Thavala va th…® ghambu ghan…®Ňčga ghambaro mava th…® vaidiya yawalinji ghathalavuwe mun.
\v 10 Mbe e la ghamba vowo, ko iyemaeŇčge vowoniye thavala va th…® kaiwo e Mevathavatha Ňägoloniye ma val…®kaiwae th…® ghana uneko.
\v 11 MbaŇča ravowovowo lagh…®ye i th…®n…®ruwo thetheghan mad…®bae e Woluwolu Bobomako Moli t…®ne na i vowo ghar…®ghar…® lenji thar…® kaiwae, ko iyemaeŇčge thetheghan…®ko th…® woraŇčgiya eto Ňčgoreiya ma ghar…®ghar…® th…® yakuwe na th…® Ňčambuwe.
\v 12 Iyake kaiwae Jisas vambe i mareva e val…®vaŇčga ma ghar…®ghar…® th…® yakuwe ‚ÄĒ e gana ghereiye na mbe ghamberegha vara e mad…®bae i vanamweŇčgiya le ghar…®ghar…® na th…® rumwaru Loi e marae.
\v 13 Iya kaiwae ghinda ra raka iteta la ghamba yakuke na ra raka e gana ghereiyeko weya Jisas na th…® vamonjinaŇčainda Ňčgoreiya amalagh…®niye va th…® vamonjinaŇčako.
\v 14 Ra iteta ghamba yakuke iyake kaiwae ghinda ma ghambanda memeghabananiye ina e yambaneke, ko iyemaeŇčge ra roroghagha ghembako iya amba i menamenako kaiwae.
\p 
\v 15 Iya kaiwae mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye weya Jisas ra giya la vowo weya Loi na vowoko iyako iye tarawa, e ghaendake ra wovavwenyevwenyeŇča amalagh…®niye idae.
\v 16 Tembe Ňčgoreiyeva, thava hu renuwaŇča valawe hu vakatha thanavu thovuye weŇčgiya ghamunena na lemi bigibigi vwelawavwelawa. Thanavu Ňčgoranjiyako Ňčgoreiya vowo Loi i warari kaiwanji.
\p 
\v 17 Hu ghambugha lemi randevivana lenji utuutu na hu yaku e lenji mbarona raberabe, kaiwae unemina ele val…®vaŇčga th…® njimbukikiŇčga na lenji kaiwoko iyako utuniye nevole th…® utuŇča weya Loi. ThoŇčgo hu ghambugha lenji utuutuko, ne weinji lenji warari th…® kaiwo; ko thoŇčgo nandere, gharenji ne i vuyowo na mane hu vaidiya thalavu thovuye lenji kaiwoko e t…®ne.
\p 
\v 18 Mbe hu naŇčgonaŇčgo kaiwame. E gharemeke t…®ne moli wo ghareghare lama vakatha i rumwaru, kaiwae mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye nuwameiya yawalimeke ghaloŇčgaloŇčga mbe i thovuye vara.
\v 19 E ghareŇčguke lagh…®ye ya naŇčgo vur…®gheghe e ghemi na hu naŇčgo weya Loi kaiwaŇčgu na i vugha kamwath…® g…®da i vaŇčgunjoghaŇčgo e ghemi.
\s1 K…®ghik…®ghi ghanaŇčgo
\p 
\v 20 Ghanda Giya Jisas mad…®bae i voru na i vaemunjoruŇča dagerawe togha memeghabananiye. Loi va i vakatha na tembe i thuweiruva mare e t…®ne na i vaŇčgurawe iye Sip gha Ranjimbukiki lagh…®ye. Iya kaiwae ya naŇčgo weya Loi, iye gharemal…®l…® gha Loi,
\v 21 i vair…®Ňčgiya thanavu thovuthovuyeke wolagh…®ye e ghemi na hu vakavakatha le renuwaŇča. Ya naŇčgowe ne i kaiwo weinda na weya Jisas Krais thanavuko iya amalagh…®niye i warariŇčako th…® yomara weinda. Ra wovavwenyevwenye amalagh…®niye mbaŇčake wolagh…®ye ma ele ghambako. Mbwana. Ňägoreiye.
\p 
\v 22 Lo bodaboda, ya naŇčgo e ghemi na wo hu vandeŇče wagiyawe lo utu vavur…®ghegheke iyake e ghemi. Letake ghautuutu iyake mbe ubotu eŇčge iya ya rorike weŇčga.
\p 
\v 23 NuwaŇčguiya wo ya giya yanawami na hu ghareghare, ghaghanda Timoti kaero mendava th…® rakayathu na i raŇčgi e thiyo t…®ne. ThoŇčgo i vamayaŇča na i vutha e ghino, tene mbaŇčarava weiŇčgu wo ghaona wo thuweŇčga.
\p 
\v 24 Hu giya lama dagemwaewoke weŇčgiya lemi randevivana wolagh…®ye na weŇčgiya Loi le ghar…®ghar…®na wolagh…®ye. RaloŇčweloŇčweghath…® th…® rakamena Itali ele val…®vaŇčga th…® mwaewo e ghemi.
\p 
\v 25 Loi ghare weŇčga taulagh…®na ghemi. 
